聞」，完全不播放及不提及：<br />\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n6.隻字不提有市民於6月15日於太古廣場因展示示威標語墮樓, 送院搶救後不治的事實<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=xNvf4PJMmDX7L7bksShbPuCrFKAYikA6kkEaryQCE%2B8%3D&h=feae251c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日期： 2019/6/12 時間1830 新聞報導</span></span>"},{"pid":"a245ce5d26f71233b12a29bd3b3d955de7fa9973","tid":1232535,"uid":113475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:26:40.000Z","msg":"真係唔好再睇TVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b082208521a07317d488d260f474494726334b8","tid":1232535,"uid":113475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:56:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba2760fe7d2cb63ec52888e7acd54308002b7381","tid":1232535,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}